hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0caa07cbf186d20adb5da059b358f28b2620ccef","tid":353222,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:54:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d32abeef75b4656e477d11aaad01430323e8f28b","tid":353222,"uid":31752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年南亞海嘯仲讀緊小學，我自發捐咗廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時對我黎講已經好多。反而四川地震個排我一個仙都無捐過，老豆仲塞500蚊畀我一定要我捐比學校再比四川，當時有一刻諗過想私吞500蚊佢，不過知道學校有收據個陣就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nkeep低果500蚊進可攻退可守<br />\n過一頭半個月先吞左佢"},{"pid":"2bd462b5fdccb9bf5e45a4db73bf96e580fa7446","tid":353222,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T17:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年南亞海嘯仲讀緊小學，我自發捐咗廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時對我黎講已經好多。反而四川地震個排我一個仙都無捐過，老豆仲塞500蚊畀我一定要我捐比學校再比四川，當時有一刻諗過想私吞500蚊佢，不過知道學校有收據個陣就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家問返佢,有無覺得當年好戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n利申：當年戇鳩,依家就睬你都戇鳩"},{"pid":"8c1caacc2c22f599d7c8f1611506d08ef32765af","tid":353222,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年南亞海嘯仲讀緊小學，我自發捐咗廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時對我黎講已經好多。反而四川地震個排我一個仙都無捐過，老豆仲塞500蚊畀我一定要我捐比學校再比四川，當時有一刻諗過想私吞500蚊佢，不過知道學校有收據個陣就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家問返佢,有無覺得當年好戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n利申：當年戇鳩,依家就睬你都戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n我直頭拎隔離post張圖比佢睇，內容係四川官員話收唔到來自香港既捐款。點知佢同我講貪既係官，中國百性係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗你真係無撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早知當年我拎去唱k韓燒用撚咗佢好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"145d1401d6cf43126534894e6fe557ce95252f1e","tid":353222,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T01:02:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年南亞海嘯仲讀緊小學，我自發捐咗廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時對我黎講已經好多。反而四川地震個排我一個仙都無捐過，老豆仲塞500蚊畀我一定要我捐比學校再比四川，當時有一刻諗過想私吞500蚊佢，不過知道學校有收據個陣就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nkeep低果500蚊進可攻退可守<br />\n過一頭半個月先吞左佢</blockquote><br />\n當時學校話一定會寄返收據比我屋企人所以我淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18cd73a004b2035d09343b116c361eb63942586","tid":353222,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"以前四川地震果時 全班得兩條友無捐錢 我係其中一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果時同班主任講 拿我依度就3毫子 我可以捐咗依3毫佢 收唔收<br />\n點知班主任叫我唔捐就唔好搞事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630d80134fd63422182243cc12d1f0c3cff76a5f","tid":353222,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前四川地震果時 全班得兩條友無捐錢 我係其中一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果時同班主任講 拿我依度就3毫子 我可以捐咗依3毫佢 收唔收<br />\n點知班主任叫我唔捐就唔好搞事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家？我拎3毫子再加多3-4蚊去搭叮叮仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b089c874039f7e2480790bafab7f00c8e1ee6567","tid":353222,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前四川地震果時 全班得兩條友無捐錢 我係其中一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果時同班主任講 拿我依度就3毫子 我可以捐咗依3毫佢 收唔收<br />\n點知班主任叫我唔捐就唔好搞事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當時幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c0b4d441405348daded9b763ded5dfa7ada7b2","tid":353222,"uid":18995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:46:25.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好憎支那 四川地震個時仲叫晒同學唔好捐<br />\n<br />\nPS 後尾個50路班主任發現左 屌到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到而家都唔覺有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fdad173cc4b9fad1bea2d550ee3549b5693614","tid":353222,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前四川地震果時 全班得兩條友無捐錢 我係其中一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果時同班主任講 拿我依度就3毫子 我可以捐咗依3毫佢 收唔收<br />\n點知班主任叫我唔捐就唔好搞事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當時幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中四 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果時個個都認自己係中國人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道有中英聯合聲明依樣嘢之後 已經覺得 點解咁嘅情況下香港會唔係獨立 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩當年無講出黎 如果唔係又被批鬥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cee4ff8d2a5d5ead3b2572824eb96be53dd193c","tid":353222,"uid":55732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前四川地震果時 全班得兩條友無捐錢 我係其中一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我果時同班主任講 拿我依度就3毫子 我可以捐咗依3毫佢 收唔收<br />\n點知班主任叫我唔捐就唔好搞事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我多你少少<br />\n俾人焗住捐咗5蚊雞<br />\n當年讀緊中二<br />\n全家一向厭支反支<br />\n所以應該成家人係得我捐咗5蚊<br />\n<br />\n後悔到而家<br />\n早知攞去買燒賣冷麵食撚咗佢算"}]}